Privacy Policy for Daily Sheets

Effective Date: August 16, 2024

1. Introduction

Welcome to Daily Sheets (“we,” “our,” “us”). We are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring that your personal information is handled in a safe and responsible manner. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard the information provided through our Discord to Instagram Image Posting Bot (the “App”).

2. Information We Collect

We collect the following types of information to provide and improve our services:

a. Information You Provide Directly:

	•	Discord Username and ID: When you interact with our bot on Discord, we collect your Discord username and ID to process your commands and respond to your requests.
	•	Instagram Access Token: To post images on your behalf, we collect and securely store the Instagram access token you provide. This token is only used to authenticate your Instagram account and publish content as instructed by you.

b. Automatically Collected Information:

	•	Log Data: We may automatically collect log information about your interactions with the App, such as the commands issued and the images selected for posting. This data is used for troubleshooting and improving the App’s performance.

3. How We Use Your Information

We use the information we collect for the following purposes:

	•	To Operate the App: We use your Discord and Instagram information to process commands, generate content, and post images to Instagram as directed by you.
	•	To Improve Our Services: We analyze usage data to understand how users interact with our App and to enhance its functionality and user experience.

4. Sharing of Information

We do not share your personal information with third parties except in the following situations:

	•	With Your Consent: We may share your information with third parties if you have given us explicit permission to do so.
	•	Legal Requirements: We may disclose your information if required by law or in response to legal processes, such as a court order or subpoena.

5. Data Security

We take the security of your information seriously and implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect it from unauthorized access, use, or disclosure. This includes encryption of sensitive data, such as your Instagram access token.

6. Your Rights

You have the following rights regarding your personal information:

	•	Access: You can request access to the personal information we hold about you.
	•	Correction: You can request that we correct any inaccuracies in your information.
	•	Deletion: You can request that we delete your information, subject to legal obligations.
	•	Opt-Out: You can opt-out of using the App at any time by ceasing interaction with the bot.

7. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or legal requirements. We will notify you of any significant changes by posting the updated policy on our website or through the App.

8. Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:

	•	Email: b3tl4b5@gmail.com
